Package: uklr
Title: Client to United Kingdom Land Registry
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: person(given = "Kostas", family = "Vasilopoulos", role =
        c("aut", "cre"), email = "k.vasilopoulo@gmail.com", comment =
        c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9769-6395"))
Description: Access data from Land Registry Open Data
        <http://landregistry.data.gov.uk/> through 'SPARQL' queries.
        'uklr' supports the house price index, transaction and price
        paid data.
